                    22seven is “read-only”, so no one can move money from your linked accounts – not even you. 
                  </mj-text>
               </mj-column> <!-- Detect Double Charge -->
                              
               <mj-column width="25%">
                  <mj-image
                     src="http://22seven-mailer.s3.amazonaws.com/images/1/shield-icon.png"
